hexo
```
npm install -g hexo-cli
```

```
mkdir <blog-folder>  
cd <blog-folder>
hexo init
```
[ZenMind](https://github.com/LenChou95/hexo-theme-ZenMind)
```
cd <blog-folder>
git clone git@github.com:LenChou95/hexo-theme-ZenMind.git themes/ZenMind
```
`_config.yml``theme``ZenMind`
```
theme: ZenMind
```
`hexo g && hexo s`githubguthub.iorepo`<blog-folder>`****`hexo g`********pushgithubrepo****repo**settings->pages->source****Deploy from a branch**branch`main`Hexo**GitHub Actions**hexo
`hexo-deploy-git`
```
npm install hexo-deployer-git --save
```
`_config.yml`
```
deploy:
    type: git 
    repository: git@github.com:usrname/usrname.github.io.git
    branch: main
```
